name: CYCLE_CRYO_EMBRYO
description: Embryos that were cryopreserved during a specific fertility treatment cycle.

columns.name: RECORD_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier for the cycle record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_ID_NAME
columns.description: A custom ID title for the cryopreservation. If not set, users will see a generated ID based on the line number, such as "Embryo N."

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_DATE
columns.description: The date that the embryos were cryopreserved.

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_DAY
columns.description: The number of days that an embryo has been in culture when it is cryopreserved.

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_STAGE_C_NAME
columns.description: The embryo's stage when it's cryopreserved.

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_FERT_METHOD_C_NAME
columns.description: The fertilization method (e.g. conventional IVF or ICSI) used for the embryo.
entries: In-Vitro Fertilization with Intra-Cytoplasmic Sperm Injection

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_AH_YN
columns.description: Whether assisted hatching was performed on the cryopreserved embryo.

columns.name: EGG_EMBRYO_GAMETE_SOURCE_C_NAME
columns.description: The cryopreserved embryo's egg source, such as if it was autologous or came from a partner or donor.

columns.name: SPERM_EMBRYO_GAMETE_SOURCE_C_NAME
columns.description: The cryopreserved embryo's sperm source, such as a partner or donor.

columns.name: EGG_EMBRYO_GAMETE_STATE_C_NAME
columns.description: The cryopreserved embryo's egg state (fresh or thawed) at the beginning of the treatment cycle.

columns.name: SPERM_EMBRYO_GAMETE_STATE_C_NAME
columns.description: The cryopreserved embryo's sperm state (fresh or thawed) at the start of the cycle.

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_EGG_DONOR
columns.description: The cryopreserved embryo's egg donor ID.

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_SPERM_DONOR
columns.description: The cryopreserved embryo's semen donor ID.

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_COMMENTS
columns.description: Comment for an embryo being cryopreserved.
